/webapi/setting/advances.TypeName: Should time worked on days off be included in the average? If the feature is not enabled, it will not be included in the average if a range that includes the day off is selected. Only if days off are selected, the average can be displayed.
The earliest starting time of the employee. If the employee starts earlier than the defined time, the start time is updated to the defined time.
The minimum working time required for an employee to be included in the average. If the employee works less than the defined time, all values are displayed as 0.
